    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>With a clear commitment to making sure every student's educational needs are met, Denver
Public Schools is comprised of 13 high schools. Now the fastest growing school district
in Colorado, this district is devoted to becoming a national leader as well as a leader in its
own state. In the last decade, the number of students enrolled in AP courses has doubled,
proving the efforts of the district have not been in vain. With constant reformation of their
education system, students learn in the best quality environment with the most effective
instruction possible. Students have access to many clubs, sports teams, AP courses and
community activities. Understanding the importance of family and community involvement
in the successful outcome of a student's future, the school district urges students to
embrace learning outside the classroom, as well as in it. Looking to achieve greatness for its
students, Denver Public Schools is guaranteed to provide a great education!</p>
